verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Wonderful name He bears,
wonderful crown He wears,
wonderful blessings His triumphs afford;
wonderful Calvary,
wonderful grace for me,
wonderful love of my wonderful Lord!{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Wonderful life, full of service so free,
friend to the poor and the needy was He;
unfailing goodness on all He bestowed,
undying faith in the vilest He showed.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Wonderful hope, He is coming again,
coming as King o’er the nations to reign;
glorious promise, His word cannot fail,
His righteous kingdom at last must prevail!{/lang-eng}
